The Questions and Answers, are familiar <lb/>
and friendly depending. The Explications, <lb/>
<normalised orig="plaine" auto="true">plain</normalised>, &amp; for the most part, concise, <lb/>
pointing at some things in a word, <lb/>
                  <pb n="3"/>
                  <lb/>
