<normalised orig="haue" auto="true">have</normalised> <normalised orig="striuen" auto="true">striven</normalised>, to be <normalised orig="plaine" auto="true">plain</normalised>, or at least, <normalised orig="hauing" auto="true">having</normalised> <lb/>
